=== EVENT_ALIEN_TRADERS ===
# id: 36
# title: Alien Traders
# chinese_title: 外星商人
# category: AlienContact
# mode: starmap

A flotilla of alien merchant ships surrounds you — not hostile, but insistent. They trade in exotic goods unseen in human space.

* [Trade credits for alien fuel cells] {requires: credits >= 8}
  ~ fuel_and_credits(6, -8)
  外星 (wàixīng) — alien
* [Trade for alien radical inscriptions]
  ~ gain_radical("外")
  铭文 (míngwén) — inscription
* [Politely decline all offers]
  ~ nothing
  谢谢 (xièxie) — thank you
